### [Isaiah Chapter 58](../../../bib/kjv/isa058.htm#001.md)

[Isaiah](../../../bib/kjv/isa001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">isa 58:0</span></span>

Overview

[Isa 58:1](../../../bib/kjv/isa058.htm#001.md), The prophet, being sent to
reprove hypocrisy, shews the difference between a counterfeit fast and a
true; [Isa 58:8](../../../bib/kjv/isa058.htm#008.md), He declares what
promises are due unto godliness, [Isa
58:13](../../../bib/kjv/isa058.htm#013.md). and to the keeping of the
sabbath.

